This package contains code adapted from the CRAN package exams
(<https://cran.r-project.org/package=exams>), which is distributed under
the GPL-2 | GPL-3 license.

In particular, parts of the ILIAS/QTI export path in this package are derived
from the upstream exams implementation in exams2ilias() and exams2qti12(),
with additional ILIAS-specific adaptations for standalone use.

